nodes.text: Six months after the Battle of Yavin, an unsavory bounty hunter gave a tip to the Galactic Empire. The tip led the Imperials to launch an attack on the Mos Eisley spaceport, located on the planet Tatooine, in order to root out their target, Rebel Luke Skywalker.
The bounty hunter was mentioned in the Official Nintendo Player's Guide released December 1, 1998. for the video game, Star Wars: Rogue Squadron.
